title: First Pwop Wok Book
text:
This is a Quarto book.
Many changes, well, one, have been made here.
To learn more about Quarto books visit https://quarto.org/docs/books.

title: 1  Introduction
text:
See Knuth (1984) for additional discussion of literate programming. See Mongeon and Paul-Hus (2016) for more info about something.




Knuth, Donald E. 1984. “Literate Programming.” Comput. J. 27 (2): 97–111. https://doi.org/10.1093/comjnl/27.2.97.


Mongeon, Philippe, and Adèle Paul-Hus. 2016. “The Journal Coverage of Web of Science and Scopus: A Comparative Analysis.” Scientometrics 106 (1): 213–28. https://doi.org/10.1007/s11192-015-1765-5.

text: In summary, this book has no content whatsoever.
